{"tid":466013,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N段歌詞形容自己愛情status","createTime":"2017-11-12T06:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T10:17:30.000Z","uid":34934,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b27b1455c3b36a9c4c66cc0b5a97f0cbb4b981","tid":466013,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"你說我未能定時<br />\n令你每天歡笑一次<br />\n我沒說出一句美麗台詞<br />\n是你心中一種缺陷定義<br />\n流進了眼角裡的刺<br />\n<br />\n為何不浪漫亦是罪名<br />\n為何不轟烈是件壞事情<br />\n從來未察覺我每個動作<br />\n沒有聲　都有愛你的鐵證<br />\n<br />\n為何苦不浪漫亦是罪名<br />\n為何總等待著特別事情<br />\n從來未察覺我語氣動聽<br />\n在我呼吸聲早已說明<br />\n甚麼都會用一生保證"},{"pid":"348a11cda636aee91a3a732b682950cdc40a9f10","tid":466013,"uid":12980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T06:59:51.000Z","msg":"我也知越是幻想不准想你更記得起"},{"pid":"1d2c2ec7b446239b375ff6e6ec62ef71c7ca13ae","tid":466013,"uid":1734,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"萊斯和勞斯都是花樣男子"},{"pid":"adde23a10f077616c71908c7b630c830830ce18c","tid":466013,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我也知越是幻想不准想你更記得起</blockquote><br />\n殘酷遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0863b8ac63c3da191e50c9021e15fb58c41497","tid":466013,"uid":34934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>萊斯和勞斯都是花樣男子</blockquote><br />\nU gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e1ff76e757a14fa2a56bc849ce5c19512ac89f","tid":466013,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:07:27.000Z","msg":"你妝都化了 要我怎麼記得"},{"pid":"be2ed33882ca49f83ba9ced341be5a8eba688302","tid":466013,"uid":12980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"難道還要抱緊這些過去<br />\n不可再進 亦不退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce26101be31